# ğŸ”” Real-Time Notification System

A standalone **real-time notification system** built with **Django, Django REST Framework, and Django Channels**, with Redis as the channel layer and Daphne as the ASGI server.  
This system can be integrated with any backend (like a ticketing system, eCommerce platform, or social app) to notify users instantly about important events.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Send notifications in real-time via WebSockets
- Redis-backed channel layer for scalability
- Support for multiple users and groups
- Event-driven design: Notifications can be triggered by signals
- Read/unread notifications support
- Easy integration with other projects

---

## ğŸ—ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Python, Django, Django REST Framework
- **Real-Time:** Django Channels, WebSockets
- **Message Broker:** Redis
- **ASGI Server:** Daphne
- **Frontend (for demo/testing):** JavaScript, Fetch API, modals (can integrate with Laravel or any frontend)

